1. *Živa* je voljela da igra lopte. (She loved to play ball.)
2. Njen otac je bio *živ*. (Her father was alive.)
3. *Žive* se uspomene od ovog vremena. (Memories of this time are alive.)
4. Ona je imala *živu* maštu. (She had a vivid imagination.)
5. *Živeli* su u malom selu. (They lived in a small village.)
6. Njeni prijatelji su bili *živi*. (Her friends were alive.)